  <p>Where this unit stands out is flexibility. You can run quick single-serve routines or larger-batch workflows depending on your schedule. The tradeoff is slightly more cleanup because hybrid systems tend to have more surfaces that can hold residue. If you are willing to rinse consistently, the convenience upside is strong.</p>
